data.description: Step into this turnkey home, built in 2008 and meticulously maintained. Situated on a serene 1-acre lot, it offers peace and privacy in abundance. The convenient one-story floor plan boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, including a private ensuite in the primary bedroom. Recent upgrades like a new roof, HVAC system, and septic make this home not only inviting but also worry-free. A full finished basement provides ample space for recreation or storage, adding versatility to the layout. Outside, you'll find a new back deck perfect for enjoying the tranquil surroundings and entertaining guests. The covered front porch adds charm and a welcoming touch. Additionally, a storage shed offers practical storage solutions. The property's highlight is its picturesque view overlooking Salt Creek, providing a serene backdrop to everyday living. With its modern amenities, spacious interiors, and idyllic setting, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort and tranquility.
